## 9. Multiple Environments

### 9.1 Parallel Installs (Dev + Prod)

**Different bundle identifiers allow both versions installed:**

```typescript
// app.config.ts
const isProduction = process.env.EXPO_PUBLIC_APP_ENV === 'production'

export default {
  name: isProduction ? 'Hestia' : 'Hestia Dev',
  slug: 'hestia',
  ios: {
    bundleIdentifier: isProduction ? 'app.justhestia.ios' : 'app.justhestia.ios.dev',
  },
  android: {
    package: isProduction ? 'app.justhestia.ios' : 'app.justhestia.ios.dev',
  },
}
```

**Result:**
- Production app: "Hestia" (app.justhestia.ios)
- Dev app: "Hestia Dev" (app.justhestia.ios.dev)
- Can install both on same device

