## 10. App Store Optimization (ASO)

### 10.1 App Store Metadata

**App Name:**
- Max 30 characters (iOS), 50 characters (Android)
- Include primary keyword
- "Hestia — Event RSVP"

**Subtitle (iOS only):**
- Max 30 characters
- Describes app purpose
- "Manage Event Invitations"

**Description:**
- First 2-3 lines most important (above "more")
- Include keywords naturally
- Focus on user benefits, not features

**Keywords (iOS only):**
- Max 100 characters
- Comma-separated
- "hestia, RSVP, event, wedding, party"

---

### 10.2 Screenshots & Previews

**Required sizes:**
- iOS: 6.5" (iPhone 14 Pro Max), 5.5" (iPhone 8 Plus)
- Android: 16:9 aspect ratio

**Best practices:**
- Show core features
- Use device frames
- Add captions explaining features
- Localize for major markets

**App preview videos (optional but recommended):**
- 15-30 seconds
- Show actual app usage
- No sound required

---

## 11. Monitoring Post-Release

### 11.1 Crash Reporting

**Sentry integration:**
- Real-time crash alerts
- Stack traces
- User impact metrics

**Thresholds:**
- Crash rate > 1% → Investigate immediately
- Crash rate > 5% → Hotfix

---

### 11.2 User Feedback

**Monitor:**
- App Store reviews
- Google Play reviews
- In-app feedback (if implemented)

**Respond to:**
- 1-star reviews (attempt to help)
- Bug reports (confirm fix timeline)
- Feature requests (thank and consider)

