## 12. Build Automation (GitHub Actions)

### 12.1 Automated Builds on Merge

**.github/workflows/deploy.yml:**
```yaml
name: EAS Build & Submit

on:
  push:
    branches: [main]

jobs:
  build:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    steps:
      - uses: actions/checkout@v4

      - name: Setup Node
        uses: actions/setup-node@v4
        with:
          node-version: '20'

      - name: Setup Expo
        uses: expo/expo-github-action@v8
        with:
          expo-version: latest
          token: ${{ secrets.EXPO_TOKEN }}

      - name: Install dependencies
        run: npm ci

      - name: Build iOS
        run: eas build --profile production --platform ios --non-interactive

      - name: Build Android
        run: eas build --profile production --platform android --non-interactive

      - name: Submit to stores
        run: |
          eas submit --platform ios --latest --non-interactive
          eas submit --platform android --latest --non-interactive
```

**Secrets to add in GitHub:**
- `EXPO_TOKEN` (from `eas login`)

