## 13. Cost Estimation

### 13.1 EAS Build Pricing (as of 2024)

**Free tier:**
- 30 builds/month
- Sufficient for early development

**Production tier ($29/month):**
- Unlimited builds
- Priority queue
- Recommended for active development

**Enterprise:** Custom pricing

---

### 13.2 App Store Fees

**Apple:**
- $99/year developer account
- 30% commission on paid apps/in-app purchases
- 15% if < $1M revenue/year (Small Business Program)

**Google:**
- $25 one-time developer account
- 30% commission on paid apps/in-app purchases
- 15% if < $1M revenue/year

