## Final Note

> **Mobile deployment is a marathon, not a sprint.**
>
> First release takes weeks (app review, metadata, testing).
> OTA updates make subsequent iterations instant.
>
> Use OTA for speed, app store for trust.

**Recommended cadence:**
- App store releases: Monthly (new features)
- OTA updates: As needed (bug fixes)

